        </a>
        <a href="/decanter-centrifuge-differential-speed/" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-gold transition-all group">
          <h3 class="text-navy font-bold group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">Decanter Differential Speed</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light mt-1">Understanding the critical relationship between bowl and conveyor speed.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/decanter-centrifuge-pond-depth/" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-gold transition-all group">
          <h3 class="text-navy font-bold group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">Decanter Centrifuge Pond Depth</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light mt-1">How pond depth affects clarification efficiency and solids dryness.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/difference-between-decanter-centrifuge-disc-centrifuge/" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-gold transition-all group">
          <h3 class="text-navy font-bold group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">Decanter vs. Disc Stack Centrifuge</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light mt-1">Key differences between the two centrifuge types and when to use each.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

